Although this approach emphasizes information related to the target entities, scaling up the set {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0054||FO}} can lead to a more diverse and comprehensive KB. The chunk size ({{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0055||FO}} in {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0056||FO}}) can be large enough to provide detailed context around the subject entity while still fitting within the LLM's context window. This setup enables a single prompt to generate a longer list of relational tuples, with the added context potentially improving entity-interaction extraction. The prompt template for Neon({{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0057||FO}}) construction is shown in (ref).